[Thank you to R. Hamilton for this contribution. Please see also E.
Boa's comment in the recent item Banana wilt - Kenya (02). If anyone
can provide actual facts on whether we are observing the spread of
two different diseases -- i.e., bacterial wilt and Panama (fungal)
wilt -- in this African region we would be most interested to hear
from them. Alternatively there may be confusion on what is what by
the different sources.
